3421:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           Temperature = ((TS_ADC_DATA - TS_CAL1)
3422:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                           * (TS_CAL2_TEMP - TS_CAL1_TEMP))
3423:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                         / (TS_CAL2 - TS_CAL1) + TS_CAL1_TEMP
3424:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           with TS_ADC_DATA = temperature sensor raw data measured by ADC
3425:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                Avg_Slope = (TS_CAL2 - TS_CAL1)
3426:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                            / (TS_CAL2_TEMP - TS_CAL1_TEMP)
3427:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                TS_CAL1   = equivalent TS_ADC_DATA at temperature
3428:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                            TEMP_DEGC_CAL1 (calibrated in factory)
3429:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                TS_CAL2   = equivalent TS_ADC_DATA at temperature
3430:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                            TEMP_DEGC_CAL2 (calibrated in factory)
3431:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Caution: Calculation relevancy under reserve that calibration
3432:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                  parameters are correct (address and data).
3433:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                  To calculate temperature using temperature sensor
3434:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                  datasheet typical values (generic values less, therefore
3435:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                  less accurate than calibrated values),
3436:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                  use helper macro @ref __LL_ADC_CALC_TEMPERATURE_TYP_PARAMS().
