3480:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Helper macro to calculate the temperature (unit: degree Celsius)
3481:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         from ADC conversion data of internal temperature sensor.
