3968:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h **** /**
3969:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC low power mode.
3970:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Description of ADC low power modes:
3971:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC low power mode "auto wait": Dynamic low power mode,
3972:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           ADC conversions occurrences are limited to the minimum necessary
3973:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           in order to reduce power consumption.
3974:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           New ADC conversion starts only when the previous
3975:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           unitary conversion data (for ADC group regular)
3976:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           or previous sequence conversions data (for ADC group injected)
3977:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           has been retrieved by user software.
3978:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           In the meantime, ADC remains idle: does not performs any
3979:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           other conversion.
3980:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           This mode allows to automatically adapt the ADC conversions
3981:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           triggers to the speed of the software that reads the data.
3982:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           Moreover, this avoids risk of overrun for low frequency
3983:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           applications.
3984:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           How to use this low power mode:
3985:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - It is not recommended to use with interruption or DMA
3986:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             since these modes have to clear immediately the EOC flag
3987:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             (by CPU to free the IRQ pending event or by DMA).
3988:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             Auto wait will work but fort a very short time, discarding
3989:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             its intended benefit (except specific case of high load of CPU
ARM GAS  /tmp/cclKt5xi.s 			page 72


3990:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             or DMA transfers which can justify usage of auto wait).
3991:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - Do use with polling: 1. Start conversion,
3992:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             2. Later on, when conversion data is needed: poll for end of
3993:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             conversion  to ensure that conversion is completed and
3994:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             retrieve ADC conversion data. This will trig another
3995:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             ADC conversion start.
3996:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   With ADC low power mode "auto wait", the ADC conversion data read
3997:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         is corresponding to previous ADC conversion start, independently
3998:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         of delay during which ADC was idle.
3999:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Therefore, the ADC conversion data may be outdated: does not
4000:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         correspond to the current voltage level on the selected
4001:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC channel.
4002:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, setting of this feature is conditioned to
4003:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC state:
4004:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC must be disabled or enabled without conversion on going
4005:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         on either groups regular or injected.
4006:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @rmtoll CFGR     AUTDLY         LL_ADC_SetLowPowerMode
4007:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @param  ADCx ADC instance
4008:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @param  LowPowerMode This parameter can be one of the following values:
4009:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @arg @ref LL_ADC_LP_MODE_NONE
4010:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @arg @ref LL_ADC_LP_AUTOWAIT
4011:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @retval None
4012:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   */
4013:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h **** __STATIC_INLINE void LL_ADC_SetLowPowerMode(ADC_TypeDef *ADCx, uint32_t LowPowerMode)
4014:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h **** {
4015:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   MODIFY_REG(ADCx->CFGR, ADC_CFGR_AUTDLY, LowPowerMode);
4016:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h **** }
