6422:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h **** /**
6423:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set mode single-ended or differential input of the selected
6424:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC channel.
6425:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Channel ending is on channel scope: independently of channel mapped
6426:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         on ADC group regular or injected.
6427:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         In differential mode: Differential measurement is carried out
6428:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         between the selected channel 'i' (positive input) and
6429:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         channel 'i+1' (negative input). Only channel 'i' has to be
6430:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         configured, channel 'i+1' is configured automatically.
6431:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Refer to Reference Manual to ensure the selected channel is
6432:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         available in differential mode.
6433:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         For example, internal channels (VrefInt, TempSensor, ...) are
6434:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         not available in differential mode.
6435:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   When configuring a channel 'i' in differential mode,
6436:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         the channel 'i+1' is not usable separately.
6437:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On STM32G4, some channels are internally fixed to single-ended inputs
6438:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         configuration:
6439:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC1: Channels 12, 15, 16, 17 and 18
6440:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC2: Channels 15, 17 and 18
6441:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC3: Channels 12, 16, 17 and 18            (1)
6442:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC4: Channels 16, 17 and 18                (1)
6443:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC5: Channels 2, 3, 4, 16, 17 and 18       (1)
6444:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         (1) ADC3/4/5 are not available on all devices, refer to device datasheet
6445:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             for more details.
6446:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   For ADC channels configured in differential mode, both inputs
6447:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         should be biased at (Vref+)/2 +/-200mV.
6448:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         (Vref+ is the analog voltage reference)
6449:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, setting of this feature is conditioned to
6450:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC state:
6451:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC must be ADC disabled.
6452:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   One or several values can be selected.
