6488:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h **** /**
6489:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Get mode single-ended or differential input of the selected
6490:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC channel.
6491:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   When configuring a channel 'i' in differential mode,
6492:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         the channel 'i+1' is not usable separately.
6493:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Therefore, to ensure a channel is configured in single-ended mode,
6494:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         the configuration of channel itself and the channel 'i-1' must be
6495:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         read back (to ensure that the selected channel channel has not been
6496:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         configured in differential mode by the previous channel).
6497:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Refer to Reference Manual to ensure the selected channel is
6498:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         available in differential mode.
6499:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         For example, internal channels (VrefInt, TempSensor, ...) are
6500:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         not available in differential mode.
6501:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   When configuring a channel 'i' in differential mode,
6502:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         the channel 'i+1' is not usable separately.
6503:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On STM32G4, some channels are internally fixed to single-ended inputs
6504:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         configuration:
6505:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC1: Channels 12, 15, 16, 17 and 18
6506:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC2: Channels 15, 17 and 18
6507:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC3: Channels 12, 16, 17 and 18            (1)
6508:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC4: Channels 16, 17 and 18                (1)
6509:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - ADC5: Channels 2, 3, 4, 16, 17 and 18       (1)
6510:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         (1) ADC3/4/5 are not available on all devices, refer to device datasheet
6511:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             for more details.
6512:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   One or several values can be selected. In this case, the value
6513:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         returned is null if all channels are in single ended-mode.
6514:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Example: (LL_ADC_CHANNEL_4 | LL_ADC_CHANNEL_12 | ...)
